title: Asymptomatic Covid19 Cases
description: A headline in a British tabloid newspaper claimed that ‘Staggering 86% who tested Covid positive in lockdown had NONE of the official symptoms’ but what does this mean and is it true?
itunes:subtitle: How many Covid19 cases are truly asymptomatic?
